The design of the entire restaurant is meant to be an experience in itself. With colorful changes of atmosphere around every turn and unique artwork inside and out, FINZ is a remarkable place to visit. That is when you'll realize what a taste of paradise is all about! Parking is never a problem. From the downstairs open-air bar and dining decks, live entertainment and waterfront view, to a formal dining room and patio upstairs, FINZ has it all. Perfect for weddings and corporate events. With numerous boat slips and updated dockage with shore power, FINZ is also a great place to visit by boat. Deep water dockage. . Built in 2005. Seating capacity is approximately 600.
